ZH: 当你在做一件事情的时候，尽力而为是非常重要的。
EN: When you are doing something, it is important to do your best.

ZH: 每个人都应该尽力而为，不要轻易放弃。
EN: Everyone should do their best and not give up easily.

ZH: 志在必得，尽力而为。
EN: Aim for success and do your best.

ZH: 他尽力而为地完成了这项任务。
EN: He did his best to complete the task.

ZH: 希望他们能尽力而为，取得成功。
EN: I hope they can do their best and succeed.

